Fy_newsealand 0.9 by Rusty9k. _____________________________ This map started out as a zombie map, hence all the hiding places and pushable props, I got bored of the whole zombie idea and turned it into a normal map. The map is based heavily of sealand, however I have no idea what the inside of sealand looks like, so I had to use my imagination! If you dont know what sealand is I reccomend you take a look at it on wikipedia, its awsome. its called new sealand just because I wanted it to sound like New Zealand :P There are a few minor bugs, but its completely playable, I will be making a new version after I get some feedback! Please enjoy the map! - Rusty _____________________________ Installation: Same as always, drop it into your maps folder. MAP DOES NOT SUPPORT BOTS! _____________________________ Please contact me at jorahill@hotmail.com if you want to do something with this map like a video or something.
